pullrequest.title: Model submission for X5 (Teambase) sensor configuration 1 from Sophisticated Engineering.

content.raw: A BaseStation (TeamBase) will be added to the Tech Repo for Cave. This BaseStation will support the intent of this PR but will not rely on an existing robot model. I'll decline this PR in deference to the forthcoming BaseStation.
